\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch People are enthusiastic about exploring aromatherapy and wish to know how to use aromatherapy essential oils for their own purposes. Aromatherapy is used for mood enhancement and promoting a sense of well being. Holistic practitioners use essential oils for treating mental health, anxiety and physical disorders including pain treatments. }{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Mix essential oils with a base oil for massages. It is important that essential oils are never directly applied to the skin in massage therapy without first mixing them in a base oil to dilute them a little. Choose a base oil (carrier oil) of olive oil, peach kernel, wheat germ, sweet almond, macadamia or jojoba oil. Mix one ounce of base oil with about three drops of the essential oil. This mixture is ideal for relaxing massages or applied to lift your moods. }{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Relax away your cares in a bath with essential oils. Many people only purchase essential oils for bathing. Add about 10 drops to a bathtub full of water and have fun experimenting with blending as many as three types of oil at once.}{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Purchase essential oil candles and place them in your favorite areas of the home. You cannot only use essential oil candles to relax, but some oils can also work to perk you up and energize. Adding a few drops to regular unscented candles will also spread the scent throughout a room.}{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Use a microwave or a pot on the stove to boil a cup of water and add a couple of drops of essential oil. Breathing in the aroma will lift your spirits and many types of essential oils help your breathing when inhaled.}{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Place essential oils in a vaporizer when you have a cold or just want to fill a room with scent. You can easily make your own vaporizer by filling a small dish with distilled water and using a candle underneath as a heat source. Use a few drops of essential oil and when it warms you will enjoy the fragrance.}{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Mix essential oils with a small portion of unscented lotion to enjoy a special fragrance. Strive for a mixture ratio of five percent lotion to two percent essential oil. }{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs17\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}}